  "slot_size": {
    "w": 66,
    "h": 66
  },
  "padding": 1,
  "pivot": "bottom-left",
  "perspective": "top-down-north-fixed",
  "category": "wall",
  "render_order": [
    "shadow  → draw wall_shadow at (wx, wy+1) when south neighbour is floor/open — drawn UNDER everything",
    "base    → draw wall_solid_normal at (wx, wy)",
    "overlay → draw wall_solid_int_* at (wx, wy) using interior adjacency bitmask"
  ],
  "notes": [
    "Shadow tile (wall_shadow_atlas.png, single slot): 64×64 transparent, darkening in top 12px only.",
    "Place shadow sprite one tile south of the wall (wy+1), rendered below floor decals and the wall itself.",
    "Only draw shadow when the wall's south neighbour is open space (not another wall tile).",
    "Base tile (col 0 of wall_atlas): fully opaque 64×64 flat square, all edges identical.",
    "Overlay tiles (cols 1-15 of wall_atlas): transparent 64×64. Interior edge bevels + face strip (bottom 10px) when s=1.",
    "Bitmask: n=8, s=4, e=2, w=1. Value 0 = no interior (skip overlay). Values 1-15 = col index."
  ],
